BR_text.BRsummary: AVX-512 detected incorrectly on macOS, compile error on older macOS versions
BR_text.BRdescription:
AVX-512 is detected incorrectly on macOS by the included version of Xbyak (typically it detects only AVX2 but it depends on whether any AVX-512 instructions were executed before, outside of oneDNN). Compilation also fails on some older macOS versions. I fixed these bugs upstream:
 <denchmark-link:https://github.com/herumi/xbyak/commit/a0c49fa2e7b0f6ff2baf7b94363304b382151cbf>herumi/xbyak@a0c49fa</denchmark-link>
 
 <denchmark-link:https://github.com/herumi/xbyak/commit/70777a69937b1ddd588e0c24091c0fd1781c0897>herumi/xbyak@70777a6</denchmark-link>
 
 Upgrading Xbyak to the latest master will fix these issues.
